::CyberShark::

    He walked down a hall, he could see the hope in her eyes. Opening the 
door the Magmatron's officehe wasn't there.
    "Magmatron, this is CyberShark, what is your location."
    "I'm on my way in, but first I need to go back and yell at the fool 
Bobertron for what he did."
    "Have you found any trace of the bots yet?"
    "You can go and look, because I've been busy."
    He went into the Communications room and looked at the screen. He saw the 
readouts.
    "It seems that Terminess has been destroyed, but it seems that Vulois is 
still alive. He is no where near the Predacon base either. Would you like me 
to take you there?"

______________________________________________________________________
::Magmatron::

    Flying back to Cheetor he found Bobertron.
    "Bobertron!! What are you doing?" Magmatron asked, he was not very 
pleased. "The Maximals will find him I am assured of it, but don't you think 
it would be a little suspisious if a Predacon gave them Cheetor? You didn't 
even finish the Destron Process, you are still Predacon. Return to base and 
let the Maximals find their 'comrade'."
